And then I have Cloud Code open in my terminal.

00:11:36.700 --> 00:11:39.460
Another slash command that is helpful is clear,

00:11:39.460 --> 00:11:41.940
which clears the context window.

00:11:41.940 --> 00:11:44.659
And say, I'm going to ask Cloud,

00:11:44.659 --> 00:11:49.659
make me a Shiny app based on the data sets provided.

00:11:52.580 --> 00:11:56.659
And so if you notice, I have to authenticate.

00:11:56.659 --> 00:11:57.900
There we go.

00:11:57.900 --> 00:12:00.260
And so if you notice here,

00:12:00.260 --> 00:12:03.659
it doesn't have a skill within this project

00:12:03.659 --> 00:12:06.940
and I don't have actually a BS Lib skill

