within my global directory.

00:12:09.739 --> 00:12:11.340
And so let's see what it does.

00:12:11.940 --> 00:12:16.940
And if it takes too long, I think we can move over.

00:12:31.539 --> 00:12:32.619
Okay, there we go.

00:12:32.619 --> 00:12:37.260
So if you notice here, it has prototyped a Shiny app for me.

